          90 is the firing point of the gun.  The value -90 are
          those points unhittable by the gun.

EXAMPLE
     Gtraj t=elevation e=600000.0 n=4920000.0 d=N34E s=15 w=M1 h=2.5a=M392 o=name

SEE ALSO
     range.place[1]

